,Recommended,218510,8992049,"Posted: 5 February, 2014",all,Ank,"Planets Under Attack is a real-time strategy game.The gameplay mechanic of Planets Under Attack are simple and not very deep, but it's good, not too easy and need some time to master. You start with a planet, build up fleets and then set out to conquer neutral or/and enemy planets. But you have to make the right decision which planet to attack first and use tactics. The first level of the game could be easy, but when you play deeper into the game, there's when the fun begin.The graphics of Planets Under Attack is cartoon, but that doesn't make the game a children game. The UI is good and well designed.Planets Under Attack is another good and fun game. I recommend this.Rating 8/10"
